Finally got the unlisted chatbot working in prod now that 24.18 is shipped. @Nathaniel, could you access this chatbot with the D&D rulebook and test a few queries? You can share with your friends to get their thoughts too. https://aihub.instabase.com/hub/apps/shared/avi.vaid/D&D%20Rulebook

Assuming the responses are generally good, let's test reddit posts once 24.20 releases since it has some quality improvements.
